        <title>Visual representation of KEGG pathway analysis for the case study.</title>
        <p>Volcano plot depicts the significance and directionality distribution for the KEGG pathway tested (−log <italic>p</italic> value vs. model coefficient). Blue (upper quadrants) represent the significantly enriched KEGG pathways and the bar graph in the volcano plot shows the overall distribution of model coefficient. Top 15 most significantly enriched KEGG pathways are labeled. Bar graph shows the top 50 enriched gene sets; the bars are model coefficient ± standard error. Only the gene sets with an FDR adjusted <italic>p</italic> &lt; 0.05 are plotted. (A) IWLS method; (B) BFGS method.</p>
