    <p>As such, the following GO term enrichment was also carried out using IWLS and FORK methods. The results showed a similar trend as that of the KEGG analysis (<xref ref-type="fig" rid="fig-4">Figs. 4</xref> and <xref ref-type="fig" rid="fig-6">6</xref>), where more GO terms with a positive model coefficient value were identified.</p>
